headline: Cintas Corporation Announces Webcast for First Quarter Fiscal Year 2026 Results
summary: CINCINNATI, September 10, 2025--Cintas Corporation (Nasdaq: CTAS) today announced that it will release fiscal year 2026 first quarter results on Wednesday, September 24, 2025. The Company will conduct a conference call to address the financial results. A live webcast of the call will be available to individual investors and the public beginning at 10:00 a.m., Eastern Time, on Wednesday, September 24, 2025.
